{"tid":158454,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"LG 將撤出支那電話市場！！","createTime":"2017-03-16T09:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T10:08:00.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0eea88b2e23cf1f83a89f49d48cc8fdb09a2f19","tid":158454,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">撤出中國手機市場！傳 LG 新旗艦機 G6 將不會在中國推出<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/15/lg-will-not-launch-g6-in-china/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2Flg-will-not-launch-g6-in-china%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a8ff22a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/15/lg-will-not-launch-g6-in-china/mobile-phone/</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n在 2017 年初手機大戰中，在暫時缺少 Samsung 這位重要對手之下，如今 LG G6 已取得一個好開始，在韓國首發銷情不俗。不過今年中國用家或可能無緣購入 LG G6 行貨，因為有消息指由於 LG 手機在中國市場佔有率極低，故此從今年開始他們可能會撤出中國市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/001-84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F001-84.jpg&h=ebf86d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據 Digitimes 引述韓國傳媒 Daum News 報導，雖然 LG 目前仍是全球著名手機品牌，比如在美國當地是第三大手機廠商，然而旗下手機在中國市場卻似乎不太受歡迎。根據 Strategy Analytics 公開的最新數據顯示，LG 現時在中國手機市場佔有率就少於 0.1%，在幾乎無利可圖的情況下，LG 在吸收過去的經驗下為避免進一步帶來巨大損失，因此今年將有可能不在中國推出新款旗艦機 G6。<br />\n<br />\n雖然中國市場龐大已是眾所周知的事，但留意當地手機市場的氣候卻有別於世界其他地區。近年中國手機絕大部份市場已被包括 Oppo、Vivo、Huawei 及 Xiaomi 等國產品牌瓜分，各大海外品牌的立足之地已日漸見少，而唯一例外就只有 Apple，iPhone 的尊貴身份成功迎合到上流人士的品味，而暫時並未看到 LG 有模仿這種風格的本錢。值得一提直到目前為止 LG 仍未宣佈會否在中國推出 G6，可見空穴來風未必無因。"},{"pid":"0e200e4888af06fb5ed874c7b38cf320b529995a","tid":158454,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16580099297bf1721d62821f81ebeea0036cc1b3","tid":158454,"uid":47027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:22:34.000Z","msg":"LG狗也不屌！"},{"pid":"e2a3d94e4a73c4e389e848b514f5836a1efea499","tid":158454,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"香港都少人用啦，而家個個都小米"},{"pid":"6f4fff1f1307d923223bc15a6aa27a7684759641","tid":158454,"uid":64060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LG狗也不屌！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那狗都不屌"},{"pid":"ee31d8e46de6730761f5e2e1f63da726f71119f1","tid":158454,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常自己國家多數買番自己品牌。</blockquote><br />\n香港例外囉 .. 所以野都係外國香 D."},{"pid":"e8d6c2588721df71e970fa4b3551814a96edb3ea","tid":158454,"uid":67278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正常自己國家多數買番自己品牌。</blockquote><br />\n香港例外囉 .. 所以野都係外國香 D.</blockquote><br />\n乜香港有自家手機品牌咩，你唔好話我知係乜鳩小米啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58543b9a81bf21ca3564a00fedc2cdee6de453ee","tid":158454,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正常自己國家多數買番自己品牌。</blockquote><br />\n香港例外囉 .. 所以野都係外國香 D.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ae9af8d33b19190092855441c465d4b510dfa5","tid":158454,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港都少人用啦，而家個個都小米</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8664e80de5d3d598d343229af98a3ec930b964f3","tid":158454,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T12:57